&quot;I thought I put that Micro SD card in my pocket, where did it go!?&quot;
Now you can carry your SD and Micro SD card around with you anywhere on this stylish key-chain holder! This part prints quickly, has little cleanup, and works great right off the bed! 
The holder has a sliding design to cover the SD cards and clips closed. To open this, pinch the back of the slider and pull when the small latches clear each other. 
Vocademy - &quot;The worlds first education based makerspace&quot;
